OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Flargely dry evening with late bright
OL,7,For sunny spells and winds falling
OL,8,Flight. Remaining dry overnight with
OL,9,Fclear spells. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA dry morning with some bright
OL,12,Fspells at first but turning
OL,13,Fincreasingly cloudy. This leads to a
OL,14,Fcloudy afternoon with rain spreading
OL,15,Feastwards later on.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
