OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy and breezy Monday and Tuesday
OL,7,Fwith the best of any bright spells in
OL,8,Fthe east. Rain at times, particularly
OL,9,Fin the west. Dry with longer sunny
OL,10,Fspells Wednesday.
